  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/a089cf53f58d5591326a68377b86108e.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the different worlds and find every secret in every one of them. Relax and enjoy the beautiful nature, while you progress the game. There are different types of worlds, for example there is a night world, a forest world and a desert type world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/335eecc8fd251bec08fac0b1eb05cd8e.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>While on your journey, you will find a lot of small stones structures, witch will tell you something about the past. They all have connection, but they are not at the exact order and it depends only on you to connect it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/0145f8db48ef9ffe85dafd553dc48ee5.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Who is the light? What is the light? What is it`s purpose? Why does it show at that time? Is it a friend? You will get an answer for these questions, through your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/027ee7c2b1420431afc2ebef8f3da76d.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Is this game for you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features about Back To Home</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a short relaxing game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a cat(it is not a cat simulator)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple connected stories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not realistic, but beautiful graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are secrets to discover </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Games like \"Firewatch\",\"Journey\", \"The First Tree\", \"Stray\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/a089cf53f58d5591326a68377b86108e.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/c72d330b27ac79ea82cdf28bc59460a6.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the different worlds and find every secret in every one of them. Relax and enjoy the beautiful nature, while you progress the game. There are different types of worlds, for example there is a night world, a forest world and a desert type world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/335eecc8fd251bec08fac0b1eb05cd8e.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/8ddab5bd328b12e2c807f2e8ac41131f.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>While on your journey, you will find a lot of small stones structures, witch will tell you something about the past. They all have connection, but they are not at the exact order and it depends only on you to connect it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/0145f8db48ef9ffe85dafd553dc48ee5.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/4b8abf585c44c26a7f73db60f2938124.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Who is the light? What is the light? What is it`s purpose? Why does it show at that time? Is it a friend? You will get an answer for these questions, through your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/027ee7c2b1420431afc2ebef8f3da76d.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.poster.avif?t=1737619252\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.webm?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469590/extras/309b243a1d7cafa79bfb5aba682f385b.mp4?t=1737619252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Is this game for you?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features about Back To Home</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a short relaxing game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a cat(it is not a cat simulator)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple connected stories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not realistic, but beautiful graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are secrets to discover </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Games like \"Firewatch\",\"Journey\", \"The First Tree\", \"Stray\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats</p></li></ul>",
